parts.content:
Mathematics is a discipline focused on discovering and organizing methods, theories, and theorems, which are developed and proven to meet the needs of both empirical sciences and the field of mathematics itself. It encompasses various areas, including number theory, algebra, geometry, analysis, and set theory.

For more detailed information, you can visit the Wikipedia page on Mathematics: [Mathematics](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mathematics).
